Package: EFBA
Type: Package
Title: Empirical Frequency Band Analysis for Time Series
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Implements Empirical Frequency Band Analysis for Time Series data. Different functions are provided for the following types of time series data; nonstationary,functional, and multivariate. The publications for these metrics can be found in the README.md under citations.  
